### Welcome to NetPHY Pages.
This website makes it easy to manage your router and any other kind of devices by offering everything you need in one place, without having to search every website for answers.

### Tech Tips Anyone?
We've crafted some great tech tips for you to use. Go ahead and continue to browse through them.

### Rather Drive Stick?
If you prefer to leave on the bleeding edge, go ahead and check out our website at https://sites.google.com/site/serialtips/. In addition to the blog, the Serial Tips website offers the latest news you may not find on the blog.

### Authors and Contributors
You can find me on GitHub @netphy and also on the following links.
